model.name: Mitrophanov2011 - Mode of action of rFVIIa on thrombin generation (Update to Hockin2002 Blood Coagulation Model)

body.p: Mathematical model of blood coagulation investigating effects of varied factor VIIa on thrombin generation. Model derived from Hockin2002/Butenas2004. Butenas added two new reactions (R28 and R29) and two new parameters (k43 and k44). Here, changes to parameters k32 and k38 and TF initial conc. changed to 5e-12
